        "title": "executing a script from maven inside a multi module project",
        "body": "<p>I have this multi-module project.<\/p>\n\n<p>In the beginning of each build I would like to run some bat file.<\/p>\n\n<p>So i did the following:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;profile&gt;\n            &lt;id&gt;deploy-db&lt;/id&gt;\n            &lt;build&gt;\n                &lt;plugins&gt;\n &lt;plugin&gt;\n            &lt;groupId&gt;org.codehaus.mojo&lt;/groupId&gt;\n            &lt;artifactId&gt;exec-maven-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n            &lt;version&gt;1.1.1&lt;/version&gt;\n        &lt;/plugin&gt;\n                &lt;/plugins&gt;\n                &lt;pluginManagement&gt;\n                    &lt;plugins&gt;\n                        &lt;plugin&gt;\n                            &lt;groupId&gt;org.codehaus.mojo&lt;/groupId&gt;\n                            &lt;artifactId&gt;exec-maven-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n                            &lt;version&gt;1.1.1&lt;/version&gt;\n                            &lt;executions&gt;\n                                &lt;execution&gt;\n                                    &lt;phase&gt;validate&lt;/phase&gt;\n                                    &lt;goals&gt;\n                                        &lt;goal&gt;exec&lt;/goal&gt;\n                                    &lt;/goals&gt;\n                                    &lt;inherited&gt;false&lt;/inherited&gt;\n                                &lt;/execution&gt;\n                            &lt;/executions&gt;\n                            &lt;configuration&gt;\n                                &lt;executable&gt;../database/schemas/import_databases.bat&lt;/executable&gt;\n                            &lt;/configuration&gt;\n                        &lt;/plugin&gt;\n                    &lt;/plugins&gt;\n                &lt;/pluginManagement&gt;\n            &lt;/build&gt;\n        &lt;/profile&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>when i run the <code>mvn verify -Pdeploy-db<\/code> from the root I get this script executed over and over again in each of my modules.<\/p>\n\n<p>I want it to be executed only once, in the root module.<\/p>\n\n<p>What is there that I am missing ?<\/p>\n\n<p>Thanks<\/p>\n",
